a persona around those people.

68
00:04:55.153 --> 00:05:00.117
Now, I tend to avoid using the P word,
the persona word.

69
00:05:00.117 --> 00:05:04.431
And that has come about
because if you say persona,

70
00:05:04.431 --> 00:05:09.648
you can pretty much guarantee
someone in either the marketing

71
00:05:09.648 --> 00:05:14.060
department or
senior management will go, yeah,

72
00:05:14.060 --> 00:05:18.999
we produced a persona last year,
we can use that, right?

73
00:05:18.999 --> 00:05:23.951
But the information that they will have
on their personas will be marketing

74
00:05:23.951 --> 00:05:28.605
information and not the information
that you actually need, right?

75
00:05:28.605 --> 00:05:33.404
So you're better off creating,
calling it something like an empathy map.

76
00:05:33.404 --> 00:05:35.150
It's basically the same thing, but

77
00:05:35.150 --> 00:05:38.652
it has different information on stuff
that we need as product designers.

78
00:05:38.652 --> 00:05:40.818
So it's things like questions and tasks,

79
00:05:40.818 --> 00:05:43.055
what tasks are the user
trying to complete?

80
00:05:43.055 --> 00:05:46.569
What questions or
objections they need answering.

81
00:05:46.569 --> 00:05:47.780
Pain points.

82
00:05:47.780 --> 00:05:51.148
What pain points are users experiencing?

83
00:05:51.148 --> 00:05:51.985
Goals.

84
00:05:51.985 --> 00:05:55.400
What's users ultimate goal,
what they're trying to achieve?

85
00:05:55.400 --> 00:05:56.385
Their journey.

86
00:05:56.385 --> 00:05:59.154
Where is the user on their journey and

87
00:05:59.154 --> 00:06:02.648
what if any interactions that they had so
far?

88
00:06:02.648 --> 00:06:07.706
What's influencing them in using the app,
whether it be people,

89
00:06:07.706 --> 00:06:13.687
things, places, whatever, and
how are they feeling about the experience.

90
00:06:13.687 --> 00:06:20.157
So I tend to take each of my segments,
create an empathy map around those.

91
00:06:20.157 --> 00:06:25.846
But obviously I need to do some user
research in order to understand

92
00:06:25.846 --> 00:06:30.637
