101
00:07:05.610 --> 00:07:10.398
You can look at existing
customer feedback,

102
00:07:10.398 --> 00:07:13.674
you can look at site behavior,

103
00:07:13.674 --> 00:07:18.844
you can talk to stakeholders
within both users.

104
00:07:18.844 --> 00:07:22.241
They're a type of stakeholder,
but also internal stakeholders,

105
00:07:22.241 --> 00:07:25.826
especially people that are dealing
with customers on a regular basis.

106
00:07:25.826 --> 00:07:30.815
You can look at search analytics or
you can do competitive analysis,

107
00:07:30.815 --> 00:07:35.975
